教师和一名律师）扣为人质数周，不知道她的丈夫和三个孩子是否还活着。她所经历的经历与我们迄今为止听说过的经历不同</description><pubDate>Fri, 26 Jul 2024 22:33:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-27/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/she-spent-weeks-conversing-with-her-hamas-captors-heres-what-they-talked-about/00000190-f0b0-dda7-a9f7-f3b7161b0000</guid></item><item><title>我们属于中东吗？以色列人让黎凡特再次变得重要</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-26/ty-article/.premium/do-we-belong-in-the-middle-east-the-israelis-making-the-levant-relevant-again/00000190-efbc-d8b8-a59a-efbe88670000</link><description>本周，一名年轻女子在加沙失去了祖父，并用歌声纪念了他。此外，特拉维夫电影中心探讨了黑人剥削、Shadi Mar&amp;#39;i 在耶路撒冷电影节上大获全胜，以及为什么一个男人用电锯锯掉了他祖父的画作</description><pubDate>Fri, 26 Jul 2024 20:36:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-26/ty-article/.premium/do-we-belong-in-the-middle-east-the-israelis-making-the-levant-relevant-again/00000190-efbc-d8b8-a59a-efbe88670000</guid></item><item><title>特朗普在佛罗里达州会见内塔尼亚胡时称哈里斯对以色列的言论不尊重</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-26/ty-article/.premium/meeting-netanyahu-in-florida-trump-says-harris-remarks-on-israel-were-disrespectful/00000190-f039-d298-a592-f83b1e230000</link><description>以色列总理内塔尼亚胡在海湖庄园会见了美国前总统、共和党候选人，并表示以色列代表团将于下周启程，继续进行人质和停火协议谈判</description><pubDate>Fri, 26 Jul 2024 18:57:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-26/ty-article/.premium/meeting-netanyahu-in-florida-trump-says-harris-remarks-on-israel-were-disrespectful/00000190-f039-d298-a592-f83b1e230000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡过时、挥霍的飞机必须下架</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-07-26/ty-article-opinion/.premium/netanyahus-outdated-profligate-plane-has-to-go/00000190-ef22-d298-a592-ff3395bf0000</link><description></description><pubDate>Fri, 26 Jul 2024 18:26:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-07-26/ty-article-opinion/.premium/netanyahus-outdated-profligate-plane-has-to-go/00000190-ef22-d298-a592-ff3395bf0000</guid></item><item><title>摩萨德负责人率领的以色列团队将于下周前往罗马进行人质和停火谈判</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-26/ty-article/.premium/israeli-team-led-by-mossad-chief-to-travel-to-rome-next-week-for-hostage-cease-fire-talks/00000190-f03a-d541-adbc-f9fa03da0000</link><description>总理本杰明·内塔尼亚胡在佛罗里达州与美国前总统唐纳德·特朗普会面时证实了这一信息，并表示代表团将“可能在本周初”离开</description><pubDate>Fri, 26 Jul 2024 18:18:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-26/ty-article/.premium/israeli-team-led-by-mossad-chief-to-travel-to-rome-next-week-for-hostage-cease-fire-talks/00000190-f03a-d541-adbc-f9fa03da0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列战争第 294 天：约旦河西岸哈马斯领导人在以色列拘留期间死亡</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-26/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-294-hamas-leader-in-west-bank-dies-in-israeli-custody/00000190-efec-d298-a592-ffff56670001</link><description>据报道，以色列正在寻求改变当前的停战提议 ■ 以色列高级谈判代表表示，内塔尼亚胡故意试图让停战谈判陷入危机 ■ 尸体被哈马斯扣押的以色列人的父亲表示，拜登向俘虏家属表示“希望未来几天会发生一些事情” ” ■ 英国不会挑战国际刑事法院对总理内塔尼亚胡和国防部长加兰特发出逮捕令的管辖权 ■ 这是战争进入第 294 天时您需要了解的内容</description><pubDate>Fri, 26 Jul 2024 16:49:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-26/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-294-hamas-leader-in-west-bank-dies-in-israeli-custody/00000190-efec-d298-a592-ffff56670001</guid></item><item><title>“拿人质的生命做赌注”：以色列高级谈判代表称内塔尼亚胡故意在停火谈判中制造危机</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-26/ty-article/.premium/senior-israeli-negotiator-says-netanyahu-knowingly-creating-crisis-in-cease-fire-talks/00000190-ef5c-dda7-a9f7-ef7f7b210000</link><description>一名参与人质交易谈判的以色列高级官员告诉国土报，内塔尼亚胡要求建立一个防止武装人员进入加沙地带北部的机制，这是“对谈判的致命打击”</description><pubDate>Fri, 26 Jul 2024 15:07:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-26/ty-article/.premium/senior-israeli-negotiator-says-netanyahu-knowingly-creating-crisis-in-cease-fire-talks/00000190-ef5c-dda7-a9f7-ef7f7b210000</guid></item><item><title>英国不会追究国际刑事法院对内塔尼亚胡逮捕令的质疑</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-26/ty-article/.premium/u-k-wont-pursue-intl-criminal-court-challenge-to-netanyahu-arrest-warrant/00000190-eef0-d298-a592-fef3b3ad0000</link><description>英国政府正式宣布推翻前政府对国际刑事法院管辖权提出质疑的政策 ■ 一位以色列高级官员告诉《国土报》，“这是一个根本错误的决定，它扭曲了正义和真理，侵犯了所有民主国家的权利”打击恐怖主义。</description><pubDate>Fri, 26 Jul 2024 12:46:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-26/ty-article/.premium/u-k-wont-pursue-intl-criminal-court-challenge-to-netanyahu-arrest-warrant/00000190-eef0-d298-a592-fef3b3ad0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列士兵在加沙地带南部丧生</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-26/ty-article/.premium/israeli-soldier-killed-in-southern-gaza-strip/00000190-eded-d45d-a5b3-efef90a90000</link><description>37岁，下士。 （res.）莫蒂·拉夫（Moti Rave）是一名推土机操作员，也是两个女孩的父亲，于周四被杀</description><pubDate>Fri, 26 Jul 2024 08:41:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-26/ty-article/.premium/israeli-soldier-killed-in-southern-gaza-strip/00000190-eded-d45d-a5b3-efef90a90000</guid></item><item><title>官员表示，以色列对英国新政府对国际刑事法院逮捕令的立场感到失望</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-26/ty-article/.premium/israel-disappointed-with-new-u-k-govts-position-on-icc-arrest-warrants-official-says/00000190-ed70-d541-adbc-fdf01c500000</link><description>以色列高级官员表示，工党政府决定撤销国际刑事法院对总理内塔尼亚胡和加兰特的逮捕令的保留，对此深感失望</description><pubDate>Fri, 26 Jul 2024 06:32:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-26/ty-article/.premium/israel-disappointed-with-new-u-k-govts-position-on-icc-arrest-warrants-official-says/00000190-ed70-d541-adbc-fdf01c500000</guid></item><item><title>以色列高级官员警告说，哈里斯呼吁迅速结束加沙战争可能会推迟达成协议</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-26/ty-article/.premium/harris-call-for-speedy-end-to-gaza-war-could-delay-deal-senior-israeli-official-warns/00000190-ed21-d469-a39d-edb7fdfe0000</link><description>当副总统在与内塔尼亚胡会面后向记者讲述“加沙可怕的人道主义危机”时，以色列外交官感到惊讶</description><pubDate>Fri, 26 Jul 2024 04:02:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-26/ty-article/.premium/harris-call-for-speedy-end-to-gaza-war-could-delay-deal-senior-israeli-official-warns/00000190-ed21-d469-a39d-edb7fdfe0000</guid></item><item><title>在华盛顿之旅中，内塔尼亚胡看到了美国大选后等待他的是什么</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-26/ty-article/.premium/in-washington-jaunt-netanyahu-got-a-glimpse-of-what-awaits-him-after-the-u-s-election/00000190-eb54-d469-a39d-efd75b0a0000</link><description>在兴高采烈的共和党人面前，内塔尼亚胡在美国大选中选边站队，尽管方式很复杂。特朗普两次刺伤以色列总理，并暗示如果他当选总统，两国关系将会是什么样子。与此同时，以色列议会在周三下午遭遇了灾难</description><pubDate>Fri, 26 Jul 2024 03:04:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-26/ty-article/.premium/in-washington-jaunt-netanyahu-got-a-glimpse-of-what-awaits-him-after-the-u-s-election/00000190-eb54-d469-a39d-efd75b0a0000</guid></item><item><title>经过长时间的美国访问后，内塔尼亚胡将回到他无法解决也不会解决的问题</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-26/ty-article/.premium/after-a-weekend-in-miami-netanyahu-will-return-to-the-problems-he-cant-and-wont-address/00000190-eb3c-d469-a39d-efbf68de0000</link><description>以色列总理政府在极右势力的压力下呻吟，但他继续推迟人质交易 ■ 与此同时，加沙战争仍在继续，北部边境持续升温</description><pubDate>Fri, 26 Jul 2024 03:00:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-26/ty-article/.premium/after-a-weekend-in-miami-netanyahu-will-return-to-the-problems-he-cant-and-wont-address/00000190-eb3c-d469-a39d-efbf68de0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防军称，以色列战机袭击黎巴嫩南部真主党目标</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-26/ty-article-live/harris-after-netanyahu-meeting-we-cant-look-away-from-dire-humanitarian-crisis-in-gaza/00000190-ecd6-dda7-a9f7-eff7dd280000</link><description>赫尔佐格和马克龙在奥运会开幕前在巴黎会面 ■ 德黑兰拒绝以色列关于袭击法国奥运选手的警告 ■ 以色列高级官员警告称，哈里斯呼吁迅速结束加沙战争可能会推迟达成协议 ■ 世卫组织运送了超过 100 万名脊髓灰质炎患者向加沙提供疫苗以保护儿童 ■ 澳大利亚、新西兰和加拿大领导人呼吁加沙立即停火</description><pubDate>Fri, 26 Jul 2024 02:32:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-26/ty-article-live/harris-after-netanyahu-meeting-we-cant-look-away-from-dire-humanitarian-crisis-in-gaza/00000190-ecd6-dda7-a9f7-eff7dd280000</guid></item><item><title>哈里斯：我告诉内塔尼亚胡是时候结束战争并签署停火协议了</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-26/ty-article/harris-i-told-netanyahu-its-time-to-end-the-war-and-sign-a-cease-fire-deal/00000190-ec68-dda7-a9f7-ef7f982f0000</link><description>美国副总统告诉记者，她“不会对加沙人类遭受的苦难保持沉默”</description><pubDate>Fri, 26 Jul 2024 00:29:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-26/ty-article/harris-i-told-netanyahu-its-time-to-end-the-war-and-sign-a-cease-fire-deal/00000190-ec68-dda7-a9f7-ef7f982f0000</guid></item><item><title>“我不支持以色列政府，但这最终不会影响我在军队的工作”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/holylandings/2024-07-26/ty-article/.highlight/i-dont-support-israels-government-but-it-wont-affect-what-i-do-in-the-army/00000190-ec37-d469-a39d-ecb7fa2a0000</link><description>本周在本古里安机场：两名以色列应届高中毕业生努力解决既想在以色列国防军服役又不支持政府的矛盾，一个在以色列有宾至如归的家庭考虑在希腊购买一套公寓</description><pubDate>Fri, 26 Jul 2024 00:04:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/holylandings/2024-07-26/ty-article/.highlight/i-dont-support-israels-government-but-it-wont-affect-what-i-do-in-the-army/00000190-ec37-d469-a39d-ecb7fa2a0000</guid></item><item><title>弗拉基米尔·普京 (Vladimir Putin) 提供的一大波自由移民浪潮袭击了以色列</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-26/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/a-major-wave-of-liberal-immigration-has-hit-israel-courtesy-of-vladimir-putin/00000190-eb4f-d8b8-a59a-efdfa4700000</link><description>他们年轻、受过教育、自由，逃离普京统治下的俄罗斯寻求自由，并大批抵达以色列。以色列会给他们足够的理由留下来吗？它们会如何影响国家的性格？新移民浪潮的故事</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Jul 2024 23:24:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-26/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/a-major-wave-of-liberal-immigration-has-hit-israel-courtesy-of-vladimir-putin/00000190-eb4f-d8b8-a59a-efdfa4700000</guid></item><item><title>亚特兰蒂斯号失落：以色列军队淹没加沙地下哈马斯隧道网络的计划如何失败</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-26/ty-article/.premium/atlantis-is-lost-how-the-israeli-armys-plan-to-flood-hamas-gaza-tunnels-failed/00000190-eb3c-d469-a39d-efbfa7ce0000</link><description>以色列一开始采用了一项陈旧且不合适的计划，随后无视专业建议和被绑架者可能面临的危险，几个月后悄然结束，有人说它是否取得了任何成果。 《国土报》的调查概述了亚特兰蒂斯计划——这是一个可预见的军事失败，直到为时已晚，没有人停止</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Jul 2024 22:27:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-26/ty-article/.premium/atlantis-is-lost-how-the-israeli-armys-plan-to-flood-hamas-gaza-tunnels-failed/00000190-eb3c-d469-a39d-efbfa7ce0000</guid></item></channel></rss>